(127, 1, '2011-04-02 03:50:20', '2011-04-02 03:50:20', 'Grand Auditorium, Conservatoire de Luxembourg\r\n\r\nAfter : read more on a)Events and b) News\r\n\r\nEnsemble M&M was founded in 2008. Ever since the double father and son duo- Jean and Gary Muller, Michel and Paul Mootz - has experienced growing success. In 2010 they engaged in the production of DVD that will be presented to the Luxembourgish public at a concert in the Conservatoire de Luxembourg on March 27, 2011. The program includes works by Gershwin, Bernstein, Rachmaninov and as a special highlight the world premiere of an arrangement of John Williams’ "Star Wars Suite" by John Williams, arranged by Jan Valta.\r\n\r\n', 'Chopin CD Release Concert, JEAN MULLER Piano Recital', 'Grand Auditorium, Conservatoire de LuxembourgDVD', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-revision-8', '', '', '2011-04-02 03:50:20', '2011-04-02 03:50:20', '', 43, 'http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/?p=127', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(128, 1, '2011-04-02 18:23:43', '2011-04-02 18:23:43', 'The young Austrian violinist Martha Khadem-Missagh, born in November 1979, started playing the violin at the age of three, gave her first public performance with five and debut as soloist with orchestra at the age of nine.\n \n    She continues the musical tradition in the fourth generation. She received first violin lessons from her father and Margarete Biedermann. She studied with Eugenia Polatschek at the Conservatory of Music Vienna, and at the Academy of Music and Performing Arts Vienna with Gerhard Schulz (Alban Berg Quartet) and Christian Altenburger. Masterclasses with Robert McDuffie, Rainer Kussmaul, Krzysztof Wegrzyn.\n \n   Concerts throughout Europe, USA, South \n\n<a href=" http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/video.mp4">video</a>\n<a href=" http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/article_bg1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-58" title="article_bg" src=" http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/article_bg1.png" alt="" width="791" height="554" /></a>', 'Martha Khadem-Missagh', 'Austria', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '54-autosave', '', '', '2011-04-02 18:23:43', '2011-04-02 18:23:43', '', 54, 'http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/?p=128', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
